{"tid":609399,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【警訊】拉素被騙200萬歐元轉會費　騙子扮飛燕諾偽造電郵追數","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T04:48:10.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7916f5a8e690f9a2fd2511502e3d38ee5e8c0f7","tid":609399,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"警訊情節發生在意甲球會拉素身上，他們輕信假電郵，被騙去200萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n騙子假扮荷甲球會飛燕諾，要求拉素將中堅迪維積的轉會費尾數入落指定戶口，拉素不虞有詐，沒有求證，就將200萬歐元入落騙子提供的戶口。<br />\n<br />\n意大利傳媒報道，意甲球會拉素中了電郵騙局，被騙去200萬歐元（約1900萬港元）。拉素在2014年以750萬歐元轉會費從飛燕諾收購荷蘭中堅迪維積（Stefan de Vrij），分期付款。當年迪維積在世界盃表現突出，故獲拉素青睞，他近4季都是拉素主將，為球隊聯賽上陣超過80次。不過，26歲的迪維積今季尾約滿，而拉素跟他的續約談判破裂，他勢必離隊。<br />\n<br />\n拉素今季需要向飛燕諾清繳迪維積的最後一期轉會費，而騙子有機可乘，冒充飛燕諾，向拉素發出一封追繳轉會費尾數的電郵。電郵像真度甚高，上面有飛燕諾的隊徽，行文用詞亦幾可亂真，故令拉素深信不疑，跌入圈套，將最後一期轉會費共200萬歐元入落騙子提供的戶口。轉賬後，拉素才起疑心，向飛燕諾查問，才發現對方根本沒有收到這筆錢，方知中了騙局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170515/large/1494854801_9cce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170515%2Flarge%2F1494854801_9cce.png&h=8ebf96e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9b3da46a8e73e2782d880b9b8494b83277a6f5e","tid":609399,"uid":159669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee01e56719ea6481cfa6f9ae3f52fce6effbb4f","tid":609399,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610e28ed974c418f0103c1876eaaba7e81372f4a","tid":609399,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9d507ce5979747c9c194c9cbd10c9d5652f633","tid":609399,"uid":69680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"意假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5518284f1d63a256dade1a173709d9c9887c043","tid":609399,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"肯定自己人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間 形式 金額吻合"},{"pid":"a4767b65b7cba7ba7a6d9495a4f924b2bf014cc4","tid":609399,"uid":67805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"收款人名稱？"}]}